    G4SAIDDATA         1.1   d88a31218fdf28455e5c5a3609f7216f  G4SAIDDATA          G4SAIDDATA         7f0c75c86eea3d227379d3dfe77e4600752f99a2  a38cd9a83db62311922850fe609ecd250d36adf264a88e88c82ba82b7da0ed7f
